When working with vas-hosting.cz infrastructure, use the `vash` CLI.
Full command reference is in `llms.txt` in this repository.

Quick reference:
- Auth:       vash auth login --name <alias> --api-key <key>
- Domains:    vash domain info <domain>
- Databases:  vash database list <domain>
- DNS:        vash dns list <domain>
- Email:      vash email list <domain>
- FTP:        vash ftp list <domain>
- Servers:    vash server list
- Labels:     vash server-label list

Always prefer --format json when parsing output programmatically.
